widget.header: Claudia Duque Gave a Conference at the Universidad La Salle Saltillo

config: In the context of "World Intellectual Property Day", Claudia Duque participated in the "Entrepreneurial Leaders SLW 2023" event at the Universidad La Salle Saltillo. She gave a conference on the importance of trademark registration. It was part of this year's World Intellectual Property Organization's (WIPO) agenda.
